{"tid":2026841,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消防員方手足還柙半年後獲准保釋","createTime":"2020-05-21T08:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T15:58:49.000Z","uid":240362,"like":272,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"7c0cad0857689d1884281ff919478bb98856ea69","tid":2026841,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"法庭文字直播台<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/5294\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F5294&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=fdc0cc55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/5294</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第三庭<br />\n#高勁修首席區域法院法官<br />\n<br />\n👥*,*,王,趙,陳(16-49)🛑趙已還押逾6個月 #聆取對控罪的回答（#1110旺角 非法集結、管有攻擊性武器、管有第I部毒藥罪等）<br />\n<br />\nA1方（33）🛑已還押逾6個月<br />\nA2 x（16）<br />\nA3陳（49）<br />\nA4趙(25)🛑已還押逾6個月<br />\nA5王(46)<br />\n<br />\n辯方一同申請押後至7月23日下午返西九三庭再答辯，因多人法援申請中<br />\n<br />\n批准押後至7月23日下午2:30分返西九三庭再答辯<br />\n<br />\n✅A1保釋申請獲批✅<br />\n<br />\n保釋條件:<br />\n現金十萬元<br />\n同事人事擔保十萬元<br />\n不離港交旅遊證件<br />\n宵禁<br />\n一週三次警署報到<br />\n居住在報稱地址，更改24小時前通知<br />\n禁足山東街西洋菜街一帶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n❌A4趙保釋申請不獲批❌<br />\n<br />\n官稱：<br />\nA4汽油彈控罪嚴重潛逃再犯風險高<br />\nA1因家人因素潛逃再犯風險低，許保釋照顧家人"},{"pid":"4dbb4b8a17f65c33a9c7e9a206987bf4aec1296e","tid":2026841,"uid":224657,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於"},{"pid":"c7dee8f6509bf22f0ea0fe3bbb6df2d2244c9cd1","tid":2026841,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dbb4b8a17f65c33a9c7e9a206987bf4aec1296e","tid":2026841,"uid":224657,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9efc07a678267109ced5de23b6f1009cca37639","tid":2026841,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:12:24.000Z","msg":"之前話要還狎既, 係咪郭X健?"},{"pid":"839e180943711476a9924e4addeb2eeb3f2341a2","tid":2026841,"uid":256142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fce714506bacf726a95789090a9bba07297cb23","tid":2026841,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e8a4fc452835b6a0ceb5077884594adce19029","tid":2026841,"uid":14918,"like":40,"dislike":4,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:13:14.000Z","msg":"紅官離地都離撚晒譜<br />\n封撚晒關點潛逃呀"},{"pid":"b17e3761ebfd67e7842e6b1687fe707970eb70e7","tid":2026841,"uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no