},{"pid":"1c071760af4290ba3aac7f37c2c056757700bae5","tid":2026841,"uid":210807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b5c0f43e0b3bfaac4caa37e748f5c6c0f34e89f","tid":2026841,"uid":56875,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:19:53.000Z","msg":"好仔唔當差 後悔吧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講到明消防"},{"pid":"a25d1043050f3aafe1bdb39f06ac672aa50dd465","tid":2026841,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c0cad0857689d1884281ff919478bb98856ea69","tid":2026841,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"法庭文字直播台<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/5294\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F5294&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=fdc0cc55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/5294</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第三庭<br />\n#高勁修首席區域法院法官<br />\n<br />\n👥*,*,王,趙,陳(16-49)🛑趙已還押逾6個月 #聆取對控罪的回答（#1110旺角 非法集結、管有攻擊性武器、管有第I部毒藥罪等）<br />\n<br />\nA1方（33）🛑已還押逾6個月<br />\nA2 x（16）<br />\nA3陳（49）<br />\nA4趙(25)🛑已還押逾6個月<br />\nA5王(46)<br />\n<br />\n辯方一同申請押後至7月23日下午返西九三庭再答辯，因多人法援申請中<br />\n<br />\n批准押後至7月23日下午2:30分返西九三庭再答辯<br />\n<br />\n✅A1保釋申請獲批✅<br />\n<br />\n保釋條件:<br />\n現金十萬元<br />\n同事人事擔保十萬元<br />\n不離港交旅遊證件<br />\n宵禁<br />\n一週三次警署報到<br />\n居住在報稱地址，更改24小時前通知<br />\n禁足山東街西洋菜街一帶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n❌A4趙保釋申請不獲批❌<br />\n<br />\n官稱：<br />\nA4汽油彈控罪嚴重潛逃再犯風險高<br />\nA1因家人因素潛逃再犯風險低，許保釋照顧家人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:50:53.000Z","msg":"但係721白衫暴動黑社會可以保釋。屌佢老母"},{"pid":"134929f589b4fd50846bc98529ebef7acfdb4c55","tid":2026841,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6a372b7d74cf36f2368e1ac024dd67843ee4aac","tid":2026841,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"501b526f60d5b0aaa531b5cf4f21a38a547b4f0f","tid":2026841,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52185615a631d5658a0eacfec5f59722bea70f54","tid":2026841,"uid":240362,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:18:08.000Z","msg":"11月19日提堂係嚴舜儀署理主任裁判官<br />\n<br />\n&quot;被告於2011年入職，曾獲消防處長嘉許，因本案被處方停職。其懷孕妻子及約30名同僚到庭旁聽，同僚透露，被告曾參與2017年颱風帕卡襲港時在飛鵝山的營救行動；他所獲發的嘉許為「消防員最高榮耀」。被告妻子得悉被告保釋被拒後，一度啜泣，雙眼通紅。&quot;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"嚴舜儀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"今次上左區院"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:52:06.000Z","msg":"12月試過向高等法院申請保釋，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">彭寶琴法官</span></strong>考慮後指被告重犯機會高，故拒絕其保釋申請。"},{"pid":"75f16ac8a81f969724d3ef0ee4e3d5f8efef8ca4","tid":2026841,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf9bed89a281393d696d0ab62be944bb24768a2","tid":2026841,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"383123163a797dcb9e8ece15956101d2749e51da","tid":2026841,"uid":111093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9213a42a7f791e4c6410cbf06d28085bd530005b","tid":2026841,"uid":320881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:54:08.000Z","msg":"政府-經濟受嚴重打擊<br />\n<br />\n封關還押-用政府資源-浪費納稅人錢<br />\n<br />\n唔還反而可以俾人地消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e998a1870c601c23f4d8ca2e5249e22895af4e63","tid":2026841,"uid":202669,"like":0,"dislike"